# some files to be ignored by stow
# This file lives in ~/.stow-global-ignore

# stow have 3 ignore files: per package(.stow-local-ignore), global(.stow-global-ignore) and default
# However, it doesn't combine all of them, so stow-global-ignore is preferred at the moment.

# Reference Docs: https://www.gnu.org/software/stow/manual/stow.html#Ignore-Lists

# --- Documentation & Metadata ---
README.md
TODO.md
TODO
